name: Da Londra i Nuovi Trend del Sesso

description:
The Weird Legend of Laguna, Ch. 1 cliffhanger ending - Nyoka slips on a vine and she falls brutally to the ground. Unfortunately, she is surrounded by a group of hostile looking faces.

Ch. 2 cliffhanger ending - Nyoka finds herself surrounded by Nazi war criminals who were never brought to justice holding spears.

The Silver Scourges of the Jungle, Ch. 1 cliffhanger ending - An explosion of dynamite sends a group of lions and a pack of tigers headed for the village where Nyoka and natives are trapped between them!
